data.title: Wolfwalkers Wolf poster by Ciaran Duffy
data.meta_description: ABOUT CIARAN Ciaran is a painter, illustrator and designer from Dundalk, Ireland and has been with Cartoon Saloon since starting as a background artist on Song of the Sea. Since then he has worked on many different projects with the studio, as co-Art Director on The Breadwinner, and concept designer on Wolf Walkers and
data.text:
Printed on Albrecht Dürer - 210 gsm

Hahnemühle Albrecht Dürer is a genuine mould-made paper made from 50% cotton and 50% α-cellulose fibres. The traditional mould-made art paper is refined with a coating specially developed for FineArt applications. The white FineArt inkjet paper does not contain optical brighteners and has a classic, strikingly defined watercolour structure that adds an artistic touch to art reproductions in particular. Combined with the matt premium inkjet coating, this produces impressive FineArt prints boasting vivid colours, deep black and optimum reproduction of detail. The acid- and lignin-free Albrecht Dürer FineArt inkjet paper meets the most exacting requirements for age resistance.
